Package org.gsma.joyn.session

This API exposes all functionality to initiate multimedia sessions between two end points based on a dedicated service ID (or feature tag).

          Description

Class Summary
MultimediaSession This class maintains the information related to a multimedia session and offers methods to manage it.
MultimediaSession.Error Image sharing error
MultimediaSession.State Multimedia session state
MultimediaSessionIntent Intent for multimedia session invitations
MultimediaSessionListener This class offers callback methods on multimedia session events
MultimediaSessionService This class offers the main entry point to initiate and manage new and existing multimedia sessions.
